# SmartFileWatcher

A modern Python application that automatically monitors and organizes files in real time.

## Features

* Real-time folder monitoring
* Automatic file categorization
* Custom user-defined rules
* Duplicate file detection
* File activity logging
* AI-ready architecture for content classification
* Cross-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS)

## Example

Input Folder:

Downloads/
├── report.pdf
├── image.png
├── notes.txt

Output Folder:

Downloads/
├── Documents/
│   └── report.pdf
├── Images/
│   └── image.png
├── Text/
│   └── notes.txt

